Cars are parked neatly along the side of the road, adding a touch of modern life to the scene. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cities. The sky itself is overcast, casting a soft, diffused light over the scene. In the distance, trees can be seen, providing a touch of nature amidst the urban setting.
